one-click-proxy.author: zzenitt
one-click-proxy.description:
The easiest and simplest way ever to browse the web anonymously!

No need to setup, configurations, subscriptions, nothing, just activate it with one click and it's done, you're browsing the web using a random proxy from any country in the world.

And very important, NO ADS, it doesn't uses a web proxy with ads like other addons, it uses HTTP and Socks proxies dynamically obtained from our proxy list.

Easiest usage than any other plugin/addon/extension. You need to know only two things:
*Over the One Click Proxy icon(at the bottom right of your screen, on Add-On bar):
  - Left click: Activate and Deactivate anonymous browsing.
  - Right click: Change the proxy that you're using.
  - On gear icon(at the right) left click to show/hide navigation toolbar button.

*Over the One Click Proxy toolbar button(at the top right of your screen, on navigation bar):
  - There's one button to activate/deactivate and another one to change the proxy IP address that you want to use.
one-click-proxy.name: one-click-proxy
